{"tid":2119573,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020DSE][多圖] 網上買卷教學","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T20:48:10.000Z","uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7db1514cb17ea80e214e2214fa1fcbd81ca5fab5","tid":2119573,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>點解要俾錢買卷</ins></strong><br />\n- 知自己幾多分，就算5**都有分高低，買返嚟J/證明自己<br />\n- 對教書嘅人嚟講，睇你答乜會有分/扣分係個好重要嘅參考資料。非常歡迎任何人投稿數學卷俾我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://t.me/cenoc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcenoc&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtBzk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=cae90119\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cenoc</a><br />\n- 其實鍾意咪買囉，使撚理人講乜咩<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>價錢</ins></strong><br />\n第一科$400<br />\n之後每科$100 (好似係，有錯請補充)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>事前準備</ins></strong><br />\n<strong>1. 身份證Scan file (黑白/彩色)</strong><br />\n影相都得，file size有限制，如果大得濟就自己用小畫家縮細佢<br />\n<strong>2. 一部電腦</strong><br />\niPad唔知得唔得，過程中要upload file上去<br />\n<br />\n入考評局個DSE portal<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkdse.hkeaa.edu.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkdse.hkeaa.edu.hk%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtBzk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=c2a8bb78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkdse.hkeaa.edu.hk/</a><br />\n右上角登入你個考生AC<br />\n<br />\n碌落去搵Data Access Request<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6XMS6u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6XMS6u.png&h=b310473b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入下啲個人資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98DHrrY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98DHrrY.png&h=49b71b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你打完啲個人資料，同埋個驗證碼之後，畫面會load一下，然後你發現下面多咗啲嘢，亦都出現咗你報考嘅科目<br />\n<br />\n上傳身份證，揀好個file之後記得撳埋上載掣，佢唔識自動上傳<br />\n個乜鬼個人資料表格就用返框住嗰兩條link去下載，一份係sample一份係表格<br />\n兩份都要下載，佢會教你點填，填完upload，網站話唔使簽名都得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5FiKew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5FiKew.png&h=e6ca7fc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後揀點樣攞卷<br />\n1. 親身去灣仔<br />\n2. 寄去你屋企<br />\n3. 寄去郵局等你攞<br />\n我自己揀去郵局攞，因為送信條友成日擺低張卡就走咗去，連有無嘗試過撳鐘嗌我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果又等多一兩日先有<br />\n<br />\n過程好似要成個幾月，需要耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n集氣希望今年打爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f99bf6e4ff6f5918fabff8ad36e75cc02cf0f5","tid":2119573,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:05:15.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n睇吓你今年有冇滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f1d32e2f4472c169c305129bdbb3c6d525fc8d","tid":2119573,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"大家買卷後記得upload上小卒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aebe15d61127d244cc9ef8ebee481a18de872fa","tid":2119573,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2f1d32e2f4472c169c305129bdbb3c6d525fc8d","tid":2119573,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"大家買卷後記得upload上小卒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:49:44.000Z","msg":"直接俾你啦，懶得upload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de3d61088b806cedfd94fb33b6102ef79ad4cef","tid":2119573,"uid":300938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"第二科之後係$104唔係$100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c486a56b2708e750ba10e2eecc1bea5733a9d0","tid":2119573,"uid":179380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:22:59.000Z","msg":"想問可唔可以淨係買分紙嚟睇"},{"pid":"a19e747dd69aac70778358fd2ef142bd99f9fb42","tid":2119573,"uid":225635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"想問如果嗰科appeal緊咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abe9bee95dff382575d16d5d36981b78b8c1ba2","tid":2119573,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a19e747dd69aac70778358fd2ef142bd99f9fb42","tid":2119573,"uid":225635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"想問如果嗰科appeal緊咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:30:00.000Z","msg":"而家都可以照買卷<br />\n只不過會喺appeal結果公佈後40日內先收到。"},{"pid":"91cc107597d698d1071cb0ad73753ac819e388f2","tid":2119573,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a135702fabda644540193bfb077e6fd55d9d1b8c","tid":2119573,"uid":225635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1abe9bee95dff382575d16d5d36981b78b8c1ba2","tid":2119573,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a19e747dd69aac70778358fd2ef142bd99f9fb42","tid":2119573,"uid":225635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"想問如果嗰科appeal緊咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:30:00.000Z","msg":"而家都可以照買卷<br />\n只不過會喺appeal結果公佈後40日內先收到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fdb0bc3d71fea480b904d484c262